WEBVTT

00:07:28.932 --> 00:07:30.265
Train your managers.

00:07:30.877 --> 00:07:33.536
Third, we know from research on victims

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:36.036
that without the ability
to report anonymously,

00:07:36.060 --> 00:07:38.529
the fear of consequences
is so overwhelming

00:07:38.553 --> 00:07:41.339
that most people
will never report incidents.

00:07:41.363 --> 00:07:43.649
We found the same was true for witnesses.

00:07:43.673 --> 00:07:46.331
When we asked them directly, in our study,

00:07:46.355 --> 00:07:48.498
whether organizations could do something

00:07:48.522 --> 00:07:51.180
to improve the fact
that they might report,

00:07:51.204 --> 00:07:53.466
they said, number one
that they could do better

00:07:53.490 --> 00:07:55.823
was allowing for witness anonymity.

00:07:56.238 --> 00:07:59.936
Second was providing choices
about who to report to.

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:01.111
